Quite a few.

4
00:03:19,950 --> 00:03:21,451
What do they say?

5
00:03:22,995 --> 00:03:24,288
The usual.

6
00:03:24,955 --> 00:03:26,707
"Death to Rosenberg."

7
00:03:26,957 --> 00:03:28,792
"Retire Rosenberg."

8
00:03:29,668 --> 00:03:31,461
"Cut off the oxygen."

9
00:03:32,963 --> 00:03:34,965
That's my favorite.

10
00:03:37,342 --> 00:03:39,553
Of course, you, Mr. Grantham...

11
00:03:39,803 --> 00:03:42,681
...did pretty good by me
your last time out.

12
00:03:43,807 --> 00:03:47,186
"Rosenberg equals the government
over business...

13
00:03:47,477 --> 00:03:51,648
...the individual over government,
the environment over everything...

14
00:03:51,940 --> 00:03:54,735
...and the Indians, oh,
give them whatever they want."

15
00:03:55,319 --> 00:03:58,822
With all due respect,
that wasn't my line, that was a quote.

16
00:03:59,031 --> 00:04:02,868
From one of your unnamed
Senior White House officials.

17
00:04:03,160 --> 00:04:05,871
Senior White House bastard,
you should have said.

18
00:04:06,163 --> 00:04:07,539
Got in there by...

19
00:04:07,831 --> 00:04:10,876
...stirring up these people,
one against the other.

20
00:04:13,003 --> 00:04:15,464
Never fails to amaze me...

21
00:04:15,672 --> 00:04:19,384
...what a man will do
to get an oval office.

22
