79
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:38,889
HOST: My goodness gracious!
I can't believe my ears!

80
00:10:39,139 --> 00:10:40,766
MALE CONTESTANT:
Hope my mom's not watching.

81
00:10:41,058 --> 00:10:42,434
HOST:
She hopes so too!

82
00:10:42,768 --> 00:10:44,228
MALE CONTESTANT:
Ma, I was just kidding.

83
00:10:44,436 --> 00:10:47,147
HOST: Ladies, have you changed
your opinion about our stud?

84
00:10:47,397 --> 00:10:49,233
You still like him?

85
00:10:49,483 --> 00:10:51,902
FEMALE CONTESTANT:
I like big guys!

86
00:10:52,236 --> 00:10:54,488
HOST:
I think your fan club has increased.

87
00:10:54,738 --> 00:10:56,240
FEMALE CONTESTANT:
Everything has increased!

