108
00:14:49,723 --> 00:14:53,185
Are these killings in any way
linked to the CIA...

109
00:14:53,477 --> 00:14:57,523
...or to any other agency
of the United States government?

110
00:14:57,814 --> 00:14:59,525
I'm shocked you'd think that.

111
00:14:59,816 --> 00:15:01,818
Bob, just look into it, okay?

112
00:15:02,152 --> 00:15:04,738
I suggest we meet back here at five.

113
00:15:05,405 --> 00:15:07,324
