live from the White House...

119
00:15:31,723 --> 00:15:34,184
...the president of the United States.

120
00:15:35,519 --> 00:15:37,271
PRESIDENT:
My fellow Americans...

121
00:15:37,729 --> 00:15:41,024
...our country has suffered
a grievous loss.

122
00:15:41,733 --> 00:15:42,943
